# 5. Write a program to perform the following operations on a string
# a. Find the frequency of a character in a string.
# b. Replace a character by another character in a string.
# c. Remove the first occurrence of a character from a string.
# d. Remove all occurrences of a character from a string.
s = input("Enter a string: ")

ch = input("Enter character to count: ")
print("Frequency:", s.count(ch))

old = input("Character to replace: ")
new = input("Replace with: ")
print("After replace:", s.replace(old, new, 1))

print("Remove first occurrence:", s.replace(ch, "", 1))
print("Remove all occurrences:", s.replace(ch, ""))
